---
// Footer.astro
---

<footer class="w-full pt-20 pb-10 px-8" id="contact">
    <div class="max-w-screen-2xl mx-auto flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-start gap-16 md:gap-0 border-b border-on-surface/20 pb-20">
        <!-- Izquierda: Título y CTA -->
        <div class="flex flex-col space-y-8 w-full md:w-1/2">
            <h2 class="font-headline text-5xl md:text-7xl font-light text-on-surface">¿En que te puedo ayudar?</h2>
            <p class="font-body text-lg text-secondary max-w-md font-light leading-relaxed">
                Siempre abierto a nuevas colaboraciones y proyectos creativos.
            </p>
            <a href="#contact" target="_blank" class="mt-4 w-fit flex items-center gap-4 bg-[#2d3435] text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-label uppercase tracking-widest text-sm hover:bg-[#2d3435]/90 hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300">
                Ponte en contacto
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm text-white">arrow_outward</span>
            </a>
        </div>

        <!-- Derecha: Enlaces y Datos -->
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-12 md:gap-24 w-full md:w-auto">
            <div class="flex flex-col space-y-6">
                <h3 class="font-label text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-outline mb-2">Redes</h3>
                <p class="font-body text-xl font-light text-on-surface flex items-center gap-2">
                    Instagram
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-col space-y-6">
                <h3 class="font-label text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-outline mb-2">Contacto</h3>
                <p class="font-body text-xl font-light text-on-surface">aleidraws@gmail.com</p>
                <p class="font-body text-xl font-light text-on-surface">+34 655 23 23 45</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="max-w-screen-2xl mx-auto mt-10 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center text-[10px] md:text-xs font-label text-outline gap-4">
        <p class="uppercase tracking-[0.2em]">© 2026 Alei</p>
        <p class="tracking-widest text-center">Pintando mis movidas, espero que te guste.</p>
    </div>
</footer>